# Download Data

https://datadryad.org/dataset/doi:10.5061/dryad.jq2bvq8kp


The key files for our paper:

microbiology_cultures_cohort.csv (257 MB) — organism, antibiotic, susceptibility (Resistant/Susceptible) ← this is our target label
microbiology_cultures_demographics.csv (34 MB) — age, gender
microbiology_cultures_ward_info.csv (49 MB) — ICU, ER, inpatient
microbiology_cultures_labs.csv (448 MB) — WBC, creatinine, etc.
